h2_title: Yaoguai King Boss Fight - Yellowbrow (Round Two)
content: He'll usually begin the next phase of the fight be performing another of his electrical cleaving attacks to tear another part of the ground, and with your low health, you'll need to quickly heal up or evade or risk an instant death!
